		<title>HOW YOU CAN WIN A SLICE OF THE DURBAN JULY MILLIONS</title>
		<link>http://www.newspages.co.za/ow-you-can-win-a-slice-of-the-durban-july-millions/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 04 Jul 2018 06:31:37 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Belanda]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Africa]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Dotcom]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Dream Moods]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Entertainment]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Events]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[KwaZulu-Natal – Government]]></category>
